Detailed Description

An (English) part of speech.

Equality, Hashing, and Copying

WNPartOfSpeech instances implement NSObject's hash and isEqual methods, as well as the NSCopying protocol. Instances may be compared by value using NSObject::isEqual: and may be used as a key in NSDictionary.
